[Auction "N"]
1S pass 2NT pass 3C pass 3D pass 4NT pass 5H pass 6S pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{This is the companion to Deal 4.

After NORTH bids 3♣ to show shortage, SOUTH makes a Control-showing bid

of 3

♦

.

NORTH no longer worries about losing two quick

♦

s. He uses

Blackwood to check for Aces, then bids 6♠.}
[BCFlags "1f"]
